						<div class="postbody">A is a more general purpose register. Math and bit operations are done with A.<br /><br />X and Y are more for an index to an array, or counting a loop. LDA array, X gets the Xth element of an array.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://nesdoug.com" class="postlink">nesdoug.com</a> -- blog/tutorial on programming for the NES</div>
